1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episode 10=

3
00:00:15,759 --> 00:00:16,559
Zuihong Parlor.

4
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:19,960
Recently, several wealthy men
in the Capital have vanished

5
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:21,960
after a night at the parlors.

6
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:24,399
Their families are being extorted.

7
00:00:25,719 --> 00:00:27,039
I asked Wu Buzhi to look into it.

8
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:30,640
All signs point to Zuihong Parlor
as the prime suspect.

9
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:33,159
What does any of this
have to do with us?

10
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,600
There is honor among thieves.

11
00:00:36,119 --> 00:00:38,000
This constant extortion

12
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:41,119
is a blatant violation
of the Martial World's code.

13
00:00:41,110 --> 00:00:43,200
They took the ransom
without releasing the hostages.

14
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:46,759
Furthermore, they are operating right
on the Sacred Hand Sect's turf.

15
00:00:48,079 --> 00:00:48,960
I want to check it out.

16
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:51,759
Just a quick look?

17
00:00:53,039 --> 00:00:55,880
They're operating in the Capital
without paying their respects to us!

18
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:57,640
Shouldn't we teach them a lesson?

19
00:00:58,320 --> 00:00:59,840
So, why are you

20
00:01:00,810 --> 00:01:01,799
discussing this with me?

21
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:05,120
I want to scout Zuihong Parlor,

22
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,760
but it is a brothel after all.

23
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,990
It would be difficult to explain
if your Auntie found out.

24
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,840
That's why

25
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:14,519
I need you to cover for me.

26
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,439
You aren't planning anything scandalous

27
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:18,480
behind my aunt's back, are you?

28
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,680
Do I really look like that kind of man?

29
00:01:22,850 --> 00:01:23,680
You'd better not be.

30
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,799
Fine, leave it to me.

31
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,040
You?

32
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:28,359
I suspect
they're from the Southern Thieves,

33
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,760
and they're likely after me.

34
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:31,760
My mood has been terrible lately anyway.

35
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:32,840
I need a distraction.

36
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:36,120
This way, please.

37
00:01:37,962 --> 00:01:38,643
Step inside!

38
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,000
Sir,

39
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:43,799
you're a new face.

40
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,290
Is this your first time here?

41
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,280
To be honest, Madam,

42
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,640
I usually have the ladies
come to my home.

43
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,760
But I've heard so much about Mei'er

44
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,120
that I had to come in person.

45
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,250
Open a private room for me.

46
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,840
Thank you for the tip, sir!

47
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,200
Please, come inside.

48
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,319
Right this way!

49
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:05,840
Please, have a seat.

50
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:08,639
I'll bring in all our loveliest girls

51
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,000
so you can take your pick.

52
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,599
Just a moment.

53
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,439
Welcome, young master!

54
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,199
Welcome.

55
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,599
Quick, come inside.

56
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,879
Is this your first visit to our parlor?

57
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,439
It's quite impressive, isn't it?

58
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,360
Gentleman,

59
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:39,080
you're certainly handsome!

60
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,240
I'd like a private room.

61
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,080
Of course.

62
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,719
Young master,

63
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,960
won't you stay for the performance?

64
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,199
I'll watch from my room.

65
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:52,080
Understood.

66
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,759
You certainly know
how to enjoy yourself.

67
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:55,879
Yes, indeed.

68
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:59,319
I'll go find the best girls for you.

69
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,199
Watch your step.

70
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:08,120
I'll show you
to the private rooms upstairs.

71
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,400
This way, please.

72
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,719
(Wushuang?)

73
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,900
(What is she doing here
at Zuihong Parlor?)

74
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,000
(Is she on the case too?)

75
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:25,240
Young master,

76
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:28,479
shall I call some girls
to keep you company?

77
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:30,800
No, no need.

78
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,120
I'd prefer to just sit by myself.

79
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,400
But people come here

80
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,280
to enjoy themselves.

81
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,120
Drinking all alone

82
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,280
is no fun.

83
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,520
I happen to like drinking alone.

84
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,400
I won't keep you.

85
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,400
Very well.

86
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,000
Enjoy yourself.

87
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:54,240
Sorry for the wait.

88
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,879
Please, have some tea.

89
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,319
(If this is a front for kidnappings,)

90
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,319
(there must be a dungeon
or a secret tunnel.)

91
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:38,639
(But where?)

92
00:04:58,090 --> 00:04:59,720
You thought that
by putting your hair up,

93
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:02,000
I wouldn't realize you're a woman?

94
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:04,279
If you came here looking for trouble,

95
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,879
you're out of your league.

96
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:07,120
Madam,

97
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:11,800
how should we deal
with this little brat?

98
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:14,720
She's all yours.

99
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:17,360
Much appreciated, Madam!

100
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,319
Thank you, Madam!

101
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,480
Buyu!

102
00:05:45,530 --> 00:05:45,959
Wushuang!

103
00:05:45,959 --> 00:05:46,959
- Buyu!
- Wushuang!

104
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:49,759
Well, well, Mao Buyu.

105
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,590
You made me stay behind to read files

106
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,600
while you snuck off
to Zuihong Parlor to have fun!

107
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:54,079
I...

108
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:55,319
Caught you red-handed, didn't I?

109
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,279
This...

110
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,040
Is that Hu Mei'er on the bed?

111
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,040
Move, let me see!

112
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:01,000
Wu...

113
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,360
Yu!

114
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:07,240
I like you, Yu!

115
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,120
Sister!

116
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:09,800
Yu!

117
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,600
Yu!

118
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:17,839
Despicable.

119
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,040
Welcome back.

120
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,319
Found anything?

121
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:31,759
Forget it.

122
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:32,879
The truth

123
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:33,800
was a total shocker.

124
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,360
Mao Buyu and Luo Wushuang

125
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,519
were having fun upstairs!

126
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,439
And there were three of them.

127
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,519
Buyu was there too?

128
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:50,600
Maybe he's here
for an investigation too.

129
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,480
Investigating?

130
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,880
Even an investigation needs limits.

131
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:55,839
Jealous, aren't you?

132
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:02,079
I think this criminal gang is different

133
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:03,040
from the usual lot.

134
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,839
Not only are they kidnapping people
on our territory,

135
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,360
but they have no ethics.

136
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,199
They take the ransom
and keep the hostages.

137
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:10,600
And then, they extort them again.

138
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,560
Someone has to teach them a lesson.

139
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:13,480
Am I right?

140
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:18,480
Are you even listening
to a word I'm saying?

141
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:20,720
No.

142
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,560
I must have been
blinded by rage earlier.

143
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,600
I should have beaten him to a pulp!

144
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:26,720
Right, right.

145
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:27,959
Go deal with the man.

146
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:30,079
I'll investigate Hu Mei'er.

147
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,279
No need.

148
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,560
I can punch him later.

149
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,240
This group is likely
from the Southern Thieves.

150
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:37,680
You lure Hu Mei'er away.

151
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,800
I'll go check her room.

152
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,439
Yes.

153
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,000
Neither of you

154
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:01,120
is allowed to speak a word
about tonight.

155
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:02,319
Relax.

156
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:04,519
I won't say anything
to tarnish your reputation.

157
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,240
What I mean is...

158
00:08:08,150 --> 00:08:10,480
the fact that I was poisoned
while investigating the place.

159
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,600
Don't you dare mention that.

160
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:13,800
It's too embarrassing.

161
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:16,439
I thought you meant something else.

162
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,319
That boss lady at Zuihong Parlor
is pure evil.

163
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,279
I can't believe she drugged me.

164
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:26,160
I'm definitely going to make her pay.

165
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:27,319
Wait.

166
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,360
I'll teach her a lesson.

167
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:32,919
Wait a minute.

168
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,960
What are you doing here anyway?

169
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,360
Looking for a pretty boy?

170
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,159
I am here on official business!

171
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,399
Not another word,

172
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,320
or I'll tear your mouth apart!

173
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:44,960
I...

174
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,159
Fine, fine.

175
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:47,480
The case comes first.

176
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,200
Look...

177
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:50,600
I'll get their attention first.

178
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,759
I'll go find Hu Mei'er.

179
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:52,360
Hold it.

180
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,480
You stay right here.

181
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,840
Don't mess with my work.

182
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:57,360
Take care of your sister.

183
00:08:57,799 --> 00:08:58,799
Leave the rest to me.

184
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,080
Master! Master!

185
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,080
How about

186
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,519
I go find Hu Mei'er myself?

187
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,960
Sir! Sir!

188
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,120
You can't just barge in!

189
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,399
Our lady is with a guest.

190
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:20,039
I don't care about guests!

191
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:21,960
I'm seeing Mei'er tonight!

192
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,279
Sheng Zi!

193
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,440
Who is it this time?

194
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,480
Oh, sir! You're back!

195
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:32,120
I want to see Mei'er.

196
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:37,120
She's with a client right now.

197
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:40,320
Do you mind waiting a while?

198
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:41,519
I do mind.

199
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:47,399
I'll arrange it right away!

200
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,879
Just a moment.

201
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:49,720
Sheng Zi!

202
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:50,799
Get the wine ready!

203
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,159
One moment, please!

204
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:03,399
Buyu has been in there for a long time.

205
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:04,759
Is he in trouble?

206
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,440
He's the only son in the Mao family.

207
00:10:07,879 --> 00:10:09,039
If anything happens to him,

208
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:11,000
it would too much for his father.

209
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,559
I can't wait.

210
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:18,679
Hold it!

211
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,840
You again?

212
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,799
I've spent a huge fortune

213
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:23,039
in this place.

214
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:24,399
If I don't see Mei'er today,

215
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,360
I'm going to lose it!

216
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,000
Go on, get out!

217
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,639
Leave!

218
00:10:28,087 --> 00:10:29,006
Sir.

219
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,000
Back so soon?

220
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,559
Don't be in such a rush.

221
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,279
You have to wait your turn.

222
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,759
I'm seeing Mei'er right now.

223
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,680
Did you bring the money?

224
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:39,440
Money?

225
00:10:42,912 --> 00:10:44,113
Gate Bureau investigation!

226
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:46,879
The Gate Bureau?

227
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,000
Can I go in now?

228
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,399
Why hide behind the screen,

229
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:24,279
Ms. Mei'er?

230
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:25,720
Are you feeling shy?

231
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,840
You're being quite forward, sir.

232
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,679
Didn't you see I was changing?

233
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:33,279
You nearly saw all of me just now.

234
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:36,000
I may be a woman of the parlors,

235
00:11:36,399 --> 00:11:38,000
but I sell my talent, not my body.

236
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:42,200
I only wish to find a good man
to share a life with.

237
00:11:43,519 --> 00:11:44,360
How do you know

238
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,159
that I'm not that man?

239
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,600
Are you truly so smitten with me, sir?

240
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,480
That you'd only marry me?

241
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,000
Naturally.

242
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:02,312
You're no gentleman.

243
00:12:02,450 --> 00:12:05,205
You're just another
philandering womanizer.

244
00:12:06,975 --> 00:12:08,054
If the flower is fragrant,

245
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,120
don't blame the bees for showing up.

246
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:11,960
Ms. Mei'er,

247
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,519
to see you tonight,

248
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:15,000
I spent a small fortune.

249
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:17,560
The night is young and fleeting.

250
00:12:17,825 --> 00:12:19,745
Why should we waste any more time?

251
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,279
Despicable!

252
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:27,320
You have a fiancée,

253
00:12:27,759 --> 00:12:29,080
yet you're here acting like a dog.

254
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,519
For the sake of your poor fiancée,

255
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:32,279
I'll castrate you!

256
00:12:32,559 --> 00:12:33,480
You aren't Hu Mei'er.

257
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:34,639
Who are you?

258
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:54,900
The Jade Squirrel.

259
00:12:55,639 --> 00:12:56,600
The one and only!

260
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:57,639
Ms. Mei'er!

261
00:12:58,087 --> 00:12:58,886
Are you in there?

262
00:13:12,325 --> 00:13:15,600
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

263
00:13:15,638 --> 00:13:18,513
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

264
00:13:19,013 --> 00:13:24,731
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

265
00:13:25,913 --> 00:13:29,233
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

266
00:13:29,363 --> 00:13:32,283
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

267
00:13:33,451 --> 00:13:38,691
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

268
00:13:39,913 --> 00:13:42,306
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

269
00:13:42,306 --> 00:13:45,956
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

270
00:13:46,025 --> 00:13:49,515
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

271
00:13:49,613 --> 00:13:52,588
♪To the ends of time♪

272
00:13:52,588 --> 00:13:55,963
♪The moon traces your face♪

273
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:59,738
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

274
00:13:59,738 --> 00:14:05,978
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

275
00:14:06,313 --> 00:14:09,528
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

276
00:14:09,813 --> 00:14:13,351
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

277
00:14:13,638 --> 00:14:16,663
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

278
00:14:16,663 --> 00:14:19,763
♪On our way to forever♪

279
00:14:19,763 --> 00:14:23,613
♪The moon traces your face♪

280
00:14:23,613 --> 00:14:26,973
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

281
00:14:27,163 --> 00:14:33,123
♪To find you
